ts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/154398/', '', 'Papaverine, Alosetron, Isometheptene', 'Amisulpride, Droperidol, Prochlorperazine, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
